A banana seedling is created by sowing a banana tree seed in a plant pot filled with soil with a gardening trowel. Once watered, it will grow into a banana sapling. A banana sapling requires level 33 Farming to plant in a fruit tree patch.

Date Changes
10 January 2019
(update)

The watered version was graphically updated to distinguish it from the unwatered version.

30 January 2014
(update)

The watered version was renamed from "Banana seedling" to "Banana seedling (w)".

11 July 2005
(update)
  • The item was made obtainable.
  • The item was renamed from "Plant pot" to "Banana seedling".
  • The item's examine was changed from "Farming skill coming soon!"

(update)
